Joy Ride;;65;;74;;R;;It's summer break and college freshman Lewis Thomas (Paul Walker) has decided to embark on a cross-country road trip to pick up the girl of his dreams, Venna (Leelee Sobieski). But Lewis' romantic hopes hit a detour when he stops on the way to rescue his older brother, Fuller (Steve Zahn), who goads him into playing a practical joke on a lonely trucker, over a CB radio. Now, that trucker, an unseen and terrifying force known only by his CB handle, Rusty Nail, wants the last laugh and revenge.;;Mystery & thriller;;John Dahl;;2001;;Steve Zahn,Paul Walker,Leelee Sobieski,Jessica Bowman,Stuart Stone,Basil Wallace,Brian Leckner,Jim Beaver;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/joy_ride